c: 38
v: 24
t: "(Dawudi atabanje kumva undi) aravuga ati \"Rwose yaguhuguje kuba yagusabye intama yawe ngo ayongere mu ze. Kandi mu by’ukuri, abenshi mu bafatanyije imitungo barahuguzanya, uretse babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; kandi ni bo bake\". Nuko Dawudi amenya ko twamugerageje asaba imbabazi Nyagasani we, yitura hasi yubamye, anicuza (kuri Allah)"